      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "〈師古曰：「但次古人而不表今人者，其書未畢故也。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "〉",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "自書契之作，先民可得而聞者，經傳所稱，唐虞以上，帝王有號謚。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "輔佐不可得而稱矣，[1]而諸子頗言之，雖不考虖孔氏，然猶著在篇籍，歸乎顯善昭惡，勸戒後人，故博采焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "孔子曰：「若聖與仁，則吾豈敢？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "[2]又曰：「何事於仁，必也聖乎！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "[3]「未知，焉得仁？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "[4]「生而知之者，上也；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "學而知之者，又其次也；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "困而不學，民斯為下矣。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "[5]又曰：「中人以上，可以語上也。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "[6]「唯上智與下愚不移。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "[7]傳曰：譬如堯舜，禹、稷、禼與之為善則行，[8]鮌、讙兜欲與為惡則誅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "[9]可與為善，不可與為惡，是謂上智。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "桀紂，龍逢、比干欲與之為善則誅，[10]于莘、崇侯與之為惡則行。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "[11]可與為惡，不可與為善，是謂下愚。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "齊桓公，管仲相之則霸，竪貂輔之則亂。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "[12]可與為善，可與為惡，是謂中人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "因茲以列九等之序，究極經傳，繼世相次，緫備古今之略要云。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "〈張晏曰：「老子玄默，仲尼所師，雖不在聖，要為大賢，文伯之母達於禮典，動為聖人所歎，言為後世所則，而在第四。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "田單以即墨孤城復強齊之大，魯連之博通，忽於榮利，藺子申威秦王，退讓廉頗，乃在第五。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "大姬巫怪，好祭鬼神，陳人化之，國多淫祀，寺人孟子違於大雅，以保其身，旣被宮刑，怨刺而作，乃在第三。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "嫪毐上烝，昬亂禮度，惡不忍聞，乃在第七。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "其餘差違紛錯不少，略舉揚較，以起失謬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "獨馳騖於數千歲之中，旁觀諸子，事業未究，而尋遇竇氏之難，使之然乎？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "師古曰：「六家之論，輕重不同；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "百行所存，趣拾難壹。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "張氏輒申所見，掎摭班史，然其所論，又自差錯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "且年代乆遠，墳典隟亡，學者舛駮，師論分異，是以表載古人名氏，或與諸書不同。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "今則特有發明，用暢厥旨。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "自女媧以下，帝鴻以前，諸子傳記，互有舛駮，敘說不同，無所取正，大要知其古帝之號而已。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "諸人士見於史傳，彰灼可知者，無待解釋，其間幽昧者，時復及焉。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "〉",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}